Belgium Said to Postpone Bond Sale Due to Market Volatility

-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n   a n d   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 
2011-03-15T08:47:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/belgium-said-to-postpone-bond-sale-due-to-market-volatility.html
  Belgium  has postponed a sale of
bonds due June 2017 due to market volatility caused by the
earthquake in  Japan , according to two people with knowledge of
the sale.  More information on the sale will come tomorrow, the people
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
